{"word":"Thomas","slug":"thomas","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Thomas</b> <a href=\"#/G2381\">G2381</a> <br/> Called also Didymus.<br/> One of the twelve apostles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=3'>Mat 10:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=18'>Mar 3:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=15'>Luk 6:15</a><br/> Present at the raising of Lazarus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=16'>Joh 11:16</a><br/> Asks Jesus the way to the Father's house<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=14&verse=5'>Joh 14:5</a><br/> Absent when Jesus first appeared to the disciples after the resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=24'>Joh 20:24</a><br/> Skepticism of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=25'>Joh 20:25</a><br/> Sees Jesus after the resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=29'>Joh 20:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=2'>Joh 21:2</a><br/> Dwells with the other apostles in Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=14'>Act 1:14</a><br/> Loyalty of, to Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=16'>Joh 11:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=28'>Joh 20:28</a>"}]}